This is several disparate files all related to improving the experience of
playing tabletop RPGs over IRC.

scribe/
- The contents of the scribe folder deal with logging IRC conversations
- scribe.pl handles the actual logging. Requires POE::Component::IRC
- scribebak will do a daily backup of logs to folders named yyyy-mm-dd
- scribecron will run scribebak (assumes scribebak in /usr/local/bin)